<BaseLayout title="Z+ | About Us">
  <section>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Z+, headquartered in the City of London, offers one-stop career training
      services to international students in the UK. We lead the international careers training
      sector in key performance indicators such as market share, internship placement, and customer
      satisfaction.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <strong>What do you do?</strong> Z+ is an international student career business consultant.
        We help international students in the UK with career or business advancement by offering
        training and guidance to build their confidence and skills for securing interviews and
        relevant careers. We also assist early-stage entrepreneurs.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>When should we meet with you?</strong> We can help at any stage of study, but the
        best time to contact us is in the first year of university. Early engagement allows us to
        plan internships and career paths effectively.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Can you guarantee that I will get an internship I like?</strong> No one can
        ethically guarantee a particular internship, but based on our track record, we are
        confident in promising either an internship or a refund. Success depends on clients making
        good progress, being prepared to accept job opportunities, and developing the necessary
        skills.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
